long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Blueskeet updates the 'Post' button on the homepage of Bluesky to use the popular community-chosen term "Skeet", which is a portmanteau of "Sky" and "Tweet". This plugin does not collect any data whatsoever.
